    "2019; Teh Carrie F et al.",
    "2009; Table 9 Summary of qualitative findings table: Equity # Summarised review finding GRADE-CERQual Assessment of confidence Explanation of GRADE-CERQual Assessment References 17 Some participants felt that health care providers dismissed or minimized their CPLBP due to their age and often with ageist statements.",
    "They often felt that they were not taken seriously or \"fobbed off\", being told that pain was a natural consequence of ageing, and they should just \"live with it\".",
